node.text:
I have made this cake in some variation a few times in the past year and each time I love it more! Something about the neon colors with the black cocoa buttercream😍
••
••
Cake details - three layer 8” cake. I used black cocoa buttercream to get this perfect black frosting without needing a single drop of food gel. Sprinkles are the perfect mix from @manvscakes bright, neon colors are from @chefmaster and, as always, rope border using a @wiltoncakes 1M tip. 
•

But, I heard today was #nationalicecreamday so I’m definitely getting on board sharing this cake AND will definitely be enjoying an ice cream after my kiddos go to bed.
